               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The Authority has a potential requirement to place a 5 year Framework Agreement for the Repair of the Sighting System fitted to Challenger 2 vehicle. There will also be the provision for 2-1 year options should this be required and subject to satisfactory supplier performance. The Authority reserves the right to add items of a similar nature during the lifetime of the contract.</P>
